longBusinessSummary: SpectraCure AB (publ) engages in the development of cancer treatment system. It develops Q-PRO, a laser device; and IDOSE software with interstitial photodynamic therapy system for the treatment of prostate cancer. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
